{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bba6ee5ac5","title":"中共中央关于东北人民政府委员候选人问题致东北局电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"25ddbfb56c","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":3,"articleId":"bba6ee5ac5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"0b9f35b0f9","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"bba6ee5ac5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文中用宋体字排印的是毛泽东加写和改写的文字。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0fce15aafb","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于东北人民政府委员候选人问题致东北局电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"bba6ee5ac5"},{"id":"0b9f35b0f9","type":"paragraph","text":"东北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"bba6ee5ac5"},{"id":"82b6301268","type":"paragraph","text":"七月三十日电悉。关于东北人民政府委员候选人，在你们提出的四十二人中，除李六如、徐寿轩准备调离东北工作，及拟从陈龙和汪金祥两人中调出一人来中央工作外，其余三十九人我们均同意。但在此三十九人中，非党人士仅占四人，太少了，应再补充几位党外人士，如一时找不到适当的人，可留若千空额，侯政协会后，可考虑从此间派些民主人士去。此点很重要，应使党外民主人士不少于五分之一，如有四分之一则更好，希你们加以研究，并将结果电告，以凭最后决定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"bba6ee5ac5"},{"id":"ee9f257b3a","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"bba6ee5ac5"},{"id":"5645ddca71","type":"paragraph","text":"未江","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"bba6ee5ac5"}],"page":{"id":"07463ae182","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"bba6ee5ac5","start":107,"end":107}}}},"__N_SSG":true}